{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-tsx","path":"/aws-s3-cloudfront/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<h1 id=\"s3에-cloudfront-적용하기\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#s3%EC%97%90-cloudfront-%EC%A0%81%EC%9A%A9%ED%95%98%EA%B8%B0\" aria-label=\"s3에 cloudfront 적용하기 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>S3에 CloudFront 적용하기</h1>\n<p>현재 개발중인 서비스에서 이미지를 불러오는것을 S3에서 직접적으로 가져와 사용하고 있는데\n서비스 특성상 이러한 이미지와 영상과 같은 미디어 파일들을 많이 사용되는 서비스 구조라\n서비스의 구조가 많이 무거워지고 리소스 사용량이 상당히 늘어날 것 같아 캐싱을 적용하기 위해서\nAWS에서 제공하는 CDN인 CloudFront를 통해서 적용하는 과정을 알아보자.</p>\n<h2 id=\"cloudfront-생성\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#cloudfront-%EC%83%9D%EC%84%B1\" aria-label=\"cloudfront 생성 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>CloudFront 생성</h2>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/35ebd7ddbe54049c8a53fdba53be22f8/4ff83/1.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 101.35135135135135%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"1\"\n        title=\"1\"\n        src=\"/static/35ebd7ddbe54049c8a53fdba53be22f8/fcda8/1.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/35ebd7ddbe54049c8a53fdba53be22f8/12f09/1.png 148w,\n/static/35ebd7ddbe54049c8a53fdba53be22f8/e4a3f/1.png 295w,\n/static/35ebd7ddbe54049c8a53fdba53be22f8/fcda8/1.png 590w,\n/static/35ebd7ddbe54049c8a53fdba53be22f8/4ff83/1.png 843w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<ol>\n<li>CloudFront > 배포 > 생성으로 이동</li>\n<li>원본 도메인은 사용중인 S3에 대한 도메인으로 선택</li>\n</ol>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/a4fff00b9b8c2b0f7ddedec8c391dd31/d125e/2.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 56.75675675675676%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"2\"\n        title=\"2\"\n        src=\"/static/a4fff00b9b8c2b0f7ddedec8c391dd31/fcda8/2.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/a4fff00b9b8c2b0f7ddedec8c391dd31/12f09/2.png 148w,\n/static/a4fff00b9b8c2b0f7ddedec8c391dd31/e4a3f/2.png 295w,\n/static/a4fff00b9b8c2b0f7ddedec8c391dd31/fcda8/2.png 590w,\n/static/a4fff00b9b8c2b0f7ddedec8c391dd31/d125e/2.png 737w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<ul>\n<li>S3 버킷 액세스에 대한 설정인데. S3에 대한 모든 접근은 차단하고 CloudFront를 통해서만 접근이 가능하게 할려면 OAI 설정은 체크한다. </li>\n</ul>\n<p>그리고 배포를 생성함.</p>\n<h2 id=\"s3-버킷-권한-편집\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#s3-%EB%B2%84%ED%82%B7-%EA%B6%8C%ED%95%9C-%ED%8E%B8%EC%A7%91\" aria-label=\"s3 버킷 권한 편집 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>S3 버킷 권한 편집</h2>\n<p>Amzone S3 > 버킷으로 이동해서 버킷 권한을 편집한다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"json\"><pre class=\"language-json\"><code class=\"language-json\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">\"Version\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"2008-10-17\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">\"Id\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"PolicyForCloudFrontPrivateContent\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">\"Statement\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>\n        <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n            <span class=\"token property\">\"Sid\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"1\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n            <span class=\"token property\">\"Effect\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"Allow\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n            <span class=\"token property\">\"Principal\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n                <span class=\"token property\">\"AWS\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"arn:aws:iam::cloudfront:user/CloudFront Origin Access Identity OAI-Here\"</span>\n            <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n            <span class=\"token property\">\"Action\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"s3:GetObject\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n            <span class=\"token property\">\"Resource\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"arn:aws:s3:::your-s3-bucket-here/*\"</span>\n        <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n        <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n            <span class=\"token property\">\"Sid\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"2\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n            <span class=\"token property\">\"Effect\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"Allow\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n            <span class=\"token property\">\"Principal\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n                <span class=\"token property\">\"AWS\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"arn:aws:iam::cloudfront:user/CloudFront Origin Access Identity OAI-Here\"</span>\n            <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n            <span class=\"token property\">\"Action\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"s3:ListBucket\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n            <span class=\"token property\">\"Resource\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"arn:aws:s3:::your-s3-bucket-here\"</span>\n        <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>자신에 맞게 수정하여 권한을 편집한다.\nS3 버킷에 대해 <code class=\"language-text\">GetObject</code> , <code class=\"language-text\">ListBucket</code> 동작에 대한 권한을 부여하여 CloudFront가 S3 이미지를 가져올 수 있도록 한다.</p>\n<h2 id=\"s3-퍼블릭-액세스-수정\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#s3-%ED%8D%BC%EB%B8%94%EB%A6%AD-%EC%95%A1%EC%84%B8%EC%8A%A4-%EC%88%98%EC%A0%95\" aria-label=\"s3 퍼블릭 액세스 수정 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>S3 퍼블릭 액세스 수정</h2>\n<p>추가적으로 기존 백엔드 코드(예: 스프링부트)에서 S3 에 대해 이미지 리소스를 업로드하는 코드를 작성해서 S3에 대해 AccessKey와 SecretKey를 통해서 작업했다면 S3 퍼블릭 액세스를 다음과 같이 수정한다.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/914fbc946a6bf5b40da86a60df79ee25/31aff/3.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 56.75675675675676%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"3\"\n        title=\"3\"\n        src=\"/static/914fbc946a6bf5b40da86a60df79ee25/fcda8/3.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/914fbc946a6bf5b40da86a60df79ee25/12f09/3.png 148w,\n/static/914fbc946a6bf5b40da86a60df79ee25/e4a3f/3.png 295w,\n/static/914fbc946a6bf5b40da86a60df79ee25/fcda8/3.png 590w,\n/static/914fbc946a6bf5b40da86a60df79ee25/31aff/3.png 823w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>다음과 같은 설정하면은 기존 백엔드 코드에 추가적인 설정 없이 이미지를 업로드하면 S3에 올라간다.</p>\n<p>이제부턴 기존 S3 리소스 요청을 CloudFront 도메인을 통해서 수행하면된다.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>기존 URL <code class=\"language-text\">https://s3-url/image.jpeg</code></li>\n<li>적용 후 URL <code class=\"language-text\">https://cloudfront-url/image.jpeg</code></li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"cache-확인\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#cache-%ED%99%95%EC%9D%B8\" aria-label=\"cache 확인 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Cache 확인</h2>\n<p>CDN 도메인으로 변경한 후 기존 S3 리소스를 가져오듯이 요청을 보내면 다음과 같이 응답 헤더를 볼 수 있다.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 563px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/a1ba6c5f85f71c2fe14942362c34bdf1/7cb89/4.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 47.2972972972973%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"4\"\n        title=\"4\"\n        src=\"/static/a1ba6c5f85f71c2fe14942362c34bdf1/7cb89/4.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/a1ba6c5f85f71c2fe14942362c34bdf1/12f09/4.png 148w,\n/static/a1ba6c5f85f71c2fe14942362c34bdf1/e4a3f/4.png 295w,\n/static/a1ba6c5f85f71c2fe14942362c34bdf1/7cb89/4.png 563w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 563px) 100vw, 563px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">x-cache</code> 를 보면은 최초 요청은 <code class=\"language-text\">Miss from cloudfront</code> 이고 새로고침을 통해서 다시 요청을 보내면 다음과 같이 바뀐다.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 532px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/45b0197e13b19bf303df85d07a0e0cd9/89a37/5.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 54.05405405405405%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"5\"\n        title=\"5\"\n        src=\"/static/45b0197e13b19bf303df85d07a0e0cd9/89a37/5.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/45b0197e13b19bf303df85d07a0e0cd9/12f09/5.png 148w,\n/static/45b0197e13b19bf303df85d07a0e0cd9/e4a3f/5.png 295w,\n/static/45b0197e13b19bf303df85d07a0e0cd9/89a37/5.png 532w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 532px) 100vw, 532px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">Hit from cloudfront</code> 로 바뀐것을 볼 수 있고. 리소스 요청에 대한 응답 시간도 크게 줄은것을 볼 수 있다. (개인 환경과, 인터넷 속도, 이미지 크기에 따라 다름)</p>\n<p>필자는 리소스 36KB에 대해 약 120밀리세컨드로 받았고 그 후 캐싱된 이미지는 약 40밀리세컨드로 받아온 모습이다.</p>\n<p>이로써 AWS Cloudfront로 S3 리소스 캐싱 작업을 수행했고.</p>\n<h2 id=\"cloudfront---s3-요금-정책\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#cloudfront---s3-%EC%9A%94%EA%B8%88-%EC%A0%95%EC%B1%85\" aria-label=\"cloudfront   s3 요금 정책 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>CloudFront - S3 요금 정책</h2>\n<p>AWS 문서에 따르면 Cloudfront - S3 간에 전송된 데이터는 S3에서 요금이 부과되지 않는다.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://blog.kakaocdn.net/dn/dvQZ5Q/btrnFazzAb7/ttfyBK0Xn02p0BhX7b17cK/img.png\"></p>\n<p>CloudFront와 S3 간에 대한 데이터는 요금이 부과되지 않는거지 Client (인터넷) 에서 CloudFront 간에 데이터 송수신 과 HTTP 요청에 대해선 부과된다. </p>\n<p>자세한 요금은 다음 이미지를 참고하자</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://blog.kakaocdn.net/dn/bNlRAh/btrnBzNjJZb/kf5n4Yw0xlfszmzTfWNPM0/img.png\">\n<img src=\"https://blog.kakaocdn.net/dn/cVU1N0/btrnHSebQNc/TfigOAnI0JSSk3dKoB1H4K/img.png\"></p>\n<h2 id=\"레퍼런스\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EB%A0%88%ED%8D%BC%EB%9F%B0%EC%8A%A4\" aria-label=\"레퍼런스 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>레퍼런스</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://jw910911.tistory.com/110\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">https://jw910911.tistory.com/110</a></p>","excerpt":"S3에 CloudFront 적용하기 현재 개발중인 서비스에서 이미지를 불러오는것을 S3에서 직접적으로 가져와 사용하고 있는데\n서비스 특성상 이러한 이미지와 영상과 같은 미디어 파일들을 많이 사용되는 서비스 구조라 \n서비스의 구조가 많이 무거워지고 리…","tableOfContents":"<ul>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"/aws-s3-cloudfront/#s3%EC%97%90-cloudfront-%EC%A0%81%EC%9A%A9%ED%95%98%EA%B8%B0\">S3에 CloudFront 적용하기</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/aws-s3-cloudfront/#cloudfront-%EC%83%9D%EC%84%B1\">CloudFront 생성</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/aws-s3-cloudfront/#s3-%EB%B2%84%ED%82%B7-%EA%B6%8C%ED%95%9C-%ED%8E%B8%EC%A7%91\">S3 버킷 권한 편집</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/aws-s3-cloudfront/#s3-%ED%8D%BC%EB%B8%94%EB%A6%AD-%EC%95%A1%EC%84%B8%EC%8A%A4-%EC%88%98%EC%A0%95\">S3 퍼블릭 액세스 수정</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/aws-s3-cloudfront/#cache-%ED%99%95%EC%9D%B8\">Cache 확인</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/aws-s3-cloudfront/#cloudfront---s3-%EC%9A%94%EA%B8%88-%EC%A0%95%EC%B1%85\">CloudFront - S3 요금 정책</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/aws-s3-cloudfront/#%EB%A0%88%ED%8D%BC%EB%9F%B0%EC%8A%A4\">레퍼런스</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>","fields":{"slug":"/aws-s3-cloudfront/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"[AWS] S3 리소스를 CloudFront를 통해 캐싱하자","date":"Apr 05, 2023","tags":["AWS","Cache","S3","CloudFront"],"keywords":["AWS","Cache"